flowchart TD
    A([🚀 User Opens App]) --> B{API Key Present?}
    B -- Yes --> C[🟢 Live Mode\nCrewAI + GPT-4o-mini]
    B -- No --> D[🟡 Demo Mode\nRule-based feedback]
    C --> E[Select Job Role]
    D --> E
    E --> F[Click Start Interview]
    F --> G[Load 6 Role-Specific Questions]

    G --> H{More Questions?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Display Question\nwith Progress Bar]
    I --> J[User Types Answer]
    J --> K[Submit Answer]
    K --> L{Mode?}
    L -- Live --> M[CrewAI Feedback Agent\nGPT-4o-mini]
    L -- Demo --> N[Rule-Based Feedback\nLength-aware logic]
    M --> O[Display Feedback]
    N --> O
    O --> P[Save to Session History]
    P --> H

    H -- No --> Q[Show Full Summary\nAll Q&A + Feedback]
    Q --> R{Restart?}
    R -- Yes --> E
    R -- No --> S([✅ Session Complete])

    style A fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style S fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style M fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style N fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
    style C fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style D fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
